## Best Practices

1. **ReUI is default** - Always check ReUI first before falling back to Shadcn
2. **Install to packages/ui** - Use `cd packages/ui && pnpm dlx shadcn@latest add @reui/<name> --yes`
3. **Exports auto-generate** - Run on every dev/build, no manual step needed
4. **Never use --overwrite** - Unless intentionally replacing a custom component
5. **Use shared imports** - Import from `@recurse/ui/components`
6. **Fix import paths if needed** - Check generated imports match our structure
7. **Icons from @recurse/ui** - Import Lucide from `lucide-react`, Tabler from `@tabler/icons-react`

